import {Navbar,Nav,Container} from 'react-bootstrap'
import {FaUser,FaNewspaper} from 'react-icons/fa'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <header>
        <Navbar bg='grey' variant='gray' expand='lg' collapseOnSelect>
            <Container>
                <Navbar.Brand href='/'>SportP</Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls='basic-navbar-nav'/>
                <Navbar.Collapse id='basic-navbar-nav'>
                    <Nav className='me-auto'>
                        <Nav.Link href='/news'><FaNewspaper/></Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href='/login'><FaUser/></Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
    </header>
  )
}

export default Header
